00:10:08,538 --> 00:10:11,821
The first response that I had written was a lot more inflammatory.

161
00:10:13,842 --> 00:10:15,203
It was a lot more obscenities.

162
00:10:15,303 --> 00:10:19,507
And if I had posted that, the response would have been something a little bit more like

163
00:10:19,567 --> 00:10:19,827
this.

