00:11:53,869 --> 00:11:56,931
whatever, like spend more time and energy to salvage whatever

187
00:11:57,231 --> 00:12:00,092
thing you're in, or do you step away and move on?

188
00:12:00,993 --> 00:12:01,193
And so.

