00:12:03,398 --> 00:12:08,023
you know, happy ending. In our particular case with Brigador, I realized that a lot

190
00:12:08,043 --> 00:12:14,468
of those mistakes were relatively small things that I could correct. And so we dedicated

191
00:12:14,489 --> 00:12:19,153
another six months to actually fixing the game. We relaunched it and have since actually

192
00:12:19,173 --> 00:12:24,698
made it to be a properly earning title. So that worked out okay. And the...

