00:38:27,019 --> 00:38:29,883
kind of like before you decide to really double down on that effort,

709
00:38:30,283 --> 00:38:32,486
kind of what goes into that sort of thinking as to whether or not

710
00:38:33,547 --> 00:38:35,329
here comes the next project as opposed to like

711
00:38:36,010 --> 00:38:37,872
sinking all those resources back into it.

712
00:38:39,730 --> 00:38:41,571
That could be an hour on its own.

713
00:38:43,052 --> 00:38:47,795
I guess my core advice there would be to treat every game

714
00:38:47,835 --> 00:38:48,215
differently.

